code: public void testLogicalAndOfNullabilities() {     assertEquals(FALSE, Nullability.and()).     assertEquals(TRUE, Nullability.and(TRUE)).     assertEquals(FALSE, Nullability.and(FALSE)).     assertEquals(UNKNOWN, Nullability.and(UNKNOWN)).     assertEquals(UNKNOWN, Nullability.and(UNKNOWN, UNKNOWN)).     assertEquals(UNKNOWN, Nullability.and(UNKNOWN, TRUE)).     assertEquals(UNKNOWN, Nullability.and(UNKNOWN, FALSE)).     assertEquals(FALSE, Nullability.and(FALSE, FALSE)).     assertEquals(TRUE, Nullability.and(FALSE, TRUE)).     assertEquals(UNKNOWN, Nullability.and(FALSE, UNKNOWN)).     assertEquals(TRUE, Nullability.and(TRUE, TRUE)).     assertEquals(TRUE, Nullability.and(TRUE, FALSE)).     assertEquals(UNKNOWN, Nullability.and(TRUE, UNKNOWN)). }
